SECTION 4: ENTITY LIFECYCLE STATE MACHINES
ENTITY: Processing Job
State | UI Rendering Rule | Trigger
---|---|---
QUEUED | Global Overlay: "Waiting... [Position in Queue]" | Active Job > 0
DOWNLOADING | Progress bar (Blue). Text: "Extracting YouTube Audio..." | yt-dlp start
SEPARATING | Progress bar (Purple). Text: "Splitting Stems (Demucs)..." | Demucs start
TRAINING | Progress bar (Gold). Text: "Optimizing Voice Model..." | RVC Train start
CONVERTING | Progress bar (Green). Text: "Applying Voice Clone..." | Inference start
COMPLETED | Toast: "Processing Complete!" | All subprocesses finish

